#software
Selenium-webdriver 3.3.0
watir 6.2.1 (支持selenium3)
ruby 2.3
gem 2.6.7

# update gem 2.6.7
gem install --local D:\tool\Test\Ruby_Watir\gem\rubygems-update-2.6.7.gem

# install watir
gem install watir

# download webdriver and copy them to ruby\bin
IEDriverServer_x64_3.3.0, 下载地址： http://selenium-release.storage.googleapis.com/index.html
chromedriver 下载地址： http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html
Firefox driver: http://www.seleniumhq.org/ (Selenium-webdriver 3.3.0 支持 firefox48.0和之后版本)

复制IEDriverServer.exe放在C:\Ruby23\bin
复制 geckodriver.exe到放在C:\Ruby23\bin
复制 chromedriver.exee放在C:\Ruby23\bin


